    {"type":"text","id":"intuitiont","x":665,"y":190,"width":290,"height":150,"text":"Intuición:\n\nP=1.0 → L=0  (perfecto)\nP=0.659 → L=0.42 (bien)\nP=0.1 → L=2.30  (mal)\nP=0.01 → L=4.61  (muy mal)\n\nEl modelo aprende a maximizar\nP(token correcto), lo que\nequivale a minimizar L.","originalText":"Intuición:\n\nP=1.0 → L=0  (perfecto)\nP=0.659 → L=0.42 (bien)\nP=0.1 → L=2.30  (mal)\nP=0.01 → L=4.61  (muy mal)\n\nEl modelo aprende a maximizar\nP(token correcto), lo que\nequivale a minimizar L.","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"middle","strokeColor":"#78350f","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":60003,"version":1,"versionNonce":60004,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":"intuition","lineHeight":1.4},

